min, blood pressure is 150/100, and they're disoriented.","dimension":7,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.050043,0.098333,0.12014,0.12281,0.12579,0.11519,0.11344,0.075302,0.060282,0.047178,0.039923,0.031566],"unified_progress":[0.065399,0.10783,0.11049,0.1092,0.11032,0.099403,0.1006,0.079866,0.07067,0.0594,0.050407,0.03642]},{"section":6,"text":"First, I know that antipsychotics can have a lot of side effects, especially in the first few weeks.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.064241,0.10735,0.10362,0.10509,0.095431,0.089895,0.086907,0.081575,0.076336,0.076226,0.064078,0.049262],"unified_progress":[0.057378,0.091374,0.096658,0.10768,0.10049,0.096771,0.092505,0.088564,0.08024,0.078061,0.062939,0.047347]},{"section":7,"text":"The most common ones I remember are things like akathisia, dystonia, and tardive dyskinesia, but those are movement disorders.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.042057,0.068008,0.083028,0.091428,0.1001,0.10284,0.10312,0.10145,0.096009,0.085412,0.070049,0.056505],"unified_progress":[0.039026,0.06659,0.088897,0.096994,0.10256,0.1096,0.10277,0.09836,0.091526,0.08528,0.067378,0.051015]},{"section":8,"text":"This patient has rigidity, which is a type of movement issue, but it's acute.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.063079,0.083835,0.086415,0.091173,0.090775,0.092178,0.094232,0.091121,0.087586,0.082064,0.07434,0.063202],"unified_progress":[0.061296,0.080924,0.086292,0.091036,0.094437,0.096536,0.094144,0.094292,0.088786,0.08439,0.071308,0.05656]},{"section":9,"text":"So maybe it's something more immediate.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.33913,0.14896,0.068606,0.052594,0.061127,0.061399,0.0547,0.059293,0.053043,0.038726,0.039682,0.022738],"unified_progress":[0.21817,0.086436,0.065533,0.065037,0.075184,0.073316,0.092208,0.079532,0.075703,0.060806,0.055704,0.052368]},{"section":10,"text":"The fever is a big clue.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.13795,0.16071,0.112,0.093636,0.082613,0.074804,0.067355,0.061059,0.05733,0.056906,0.051934,0.043694],"unified_progress":[0.068816,0.10727,0.073445,0.093959,0.096307,0.093902,0.089558,0.086659,0.081947,0.077385,0.071148,0.059604]},{"section":11,"text":"High fever can be caused by a lot of things, but in the context of antipsychotics, I'm thinking of neuroleptic malignant syndrome (NMS).","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.056453,0.087972,0.10482,0.10927,0.10251,0.096273,0.093797,0.085465,0.078002,0.075557,0.060868,0.049012],"unified_progress":[0.041479,0.07484,0.091452,0.10081,0.10053,0.099319,0.10025,0.095822,0.089905,0.084767,0.06982,0.051008]},{"section":12,"text":"I remember that NMS is a rare but severe reaction to antipsychotics, usually within the first few weeks of treatment.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040392,0.064709,0.079737,0.086989,0.097614,0.10192,0.10265,0.10284,0.098989,0.087722,0.072866,0.063577],"unified_progress":[0.043315,0.069383,0.084793,0.093099,0.09764,0.10461,0.10205,0.099356,0.092315,0.085603,0.071139,0.056696]},{"section":13,"text":"Symptoms include high fever, muscle rigidity, confusion, and sometimes autonomic issues like increased sweating and tachycardia, which matches the patient's presentation.","dimension":9,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.050383,0.081942,0.083918,0.089782,0.090027,0.092864,0.095315,0.094443,0.09136,0.08315,0.076076,0.070741],"unified_progress":[0.057373,0.081804,0.087183,0.09036,0.092842,0.097511,0.093884,0.094976,0.088698,0.082899,0.071925,0.060547]},{"section":14,"text":"Another thought: could it be a drug reaction?","dimension":3,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.031768,0.064837,0.081788,0.095791,0.094315,0.096221,0.099923,0.099468,0.097404,0.099733,0.080521,0.058231],"unified_progress":[0.035327,0.072631,0.090489,0.10403,0.10